[1
Date: Mon, 23 Apr 2001 17:00:12 +0500
From: Rumina Hasan <rumina.hasan@aku.edu>

N.meningitidis W135 in a person returning from Saudi Arabia
----------------------------------------------------
On the 26 Mar 2001 a 62 year old male presented to our hospital with a
history of fever, weakness and loss of consciousness. _N.
meningitidis_ W135 was isolated from blood culture. CSF culture was
not requested. The patient had recently returned from Saudi Arabia
after performing Haj.
--
Rumina Hasan
Associate Professor
Depts. Microbiology/Pathology
Aga Khan University
Karachi, Pakistan
<rumina.hasan@aku.edu>
